Package de.hshn.mi.pdbg.basicservice

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicDBServiceTestCase
    BasicDBServiceTestCase is the superclass of all basic test case classes.
    BasicDBServiceTestSuite
    BasicDBServiceTestSuite provide a test suite for all basic test cases.
    HospitalStayTestCase
    HospitalStayTestCase provides methods in order to test the handling of HospitalStay objects.
    PatientTestCase
    Checks all Patient-relevant methods of the implementation of BasicDBService and Patient
    ServiceTestCase
    ServiceTestCase provides methods to test common features of a BasicDBService object.
    WardTestCase
    Checks all Ward-relevant methods of the implementation of BasicDBService and Ward
